In the voice reciting the Nembutsu there is the light of Amida waiting to
receive ali sinners. Let us pray to be embraced in the light of Amit√¢bha,
relying upon the power of the Nembutsu, which is a saving boat taking us to
the golden shore where there is the consummation of happiness.
